description:
Lunchbox thinks the company is trying to kill him after inviting him to skydive. We played a round of the Bobby Feud to see if the show can name the Top 10 best family sit down restaurants according to Americans. After revealing that he gets naked massages, Lunchbox called a massage therapist to see if it’s really that weird and the percentage of people that do.
